1
00:01:20,440 --> 00:01:21,480
It's been ages.

2
00:01:22,160 --> 00:01:23,289
Why are you still up?

3
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,600
You're up, too.

4
00:01:31,160 --> 00:01:32,890
You're checking that account?

5
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:36,680
The account for the 500,000 taels.

6
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:39,280
It was hidden in the settlement of the Bai Army's provisions,

7
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:42,610
linked to surplus subsidies from merchants in the capital.

8
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:48,800
These merchants do business with the Bai Manor,

9
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:51,720
but never had ties to the Bai Army.

10
00:01:52,479 --> 00:01:54,960
Someone did this on purpose.

11
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:58,160
Who do you think it is?

12
00:01:58,600 --> 00:01:59,560
Shen Lingbo.

13
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:00,720
Shen Lingbo.

14
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,740
It's my fault, really.

15
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:05,120
I was spending money like water back then.

16
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,720
There was a deficit of tens of thousands.

17
00:02:06,720 --> 00:02:08,520
Shen Lingbo offered

18
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:10,280
to fill the hole in the Marquis Manor's accounts.

19
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,740
I didn't ask how she did it.

20
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:13,280
It was fixed, anyway.

21
00:02:13,960 --> 00:02:15,200
Why would she do that?

22
00:02:15,880 --> 00:02:17,880
It's just a preliminary suspicion.

23
00:02:21,720 --> 00:02:23,720
Anyway, I'll get to the bottom of it.

24
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:25,640
And give you an explanation.

25
00:02:26,720 --> 00:02:28,520
When did you become so reliable?

26
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:32,320
I'm the husband of a heroine like you.

27
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,640
I have to be reliable.

28
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:36,160
Why didn't you say so before?

29
00:02:36,160 --> 00:02:38,220
I was afraid you wouldn't believe me.

30
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:41,720
Now I'm afraid you won't hear it.

31
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:43,130
What do you need me to do?

32
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:49,220
Stay with me tonight and check the accounts.

33
00:02:49,440 --> 00:02:49,840
Okay.

34
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:55,720
As the heart desires.

35
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:12,400
You bastard, why did you come back?

36
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,320
Who let you come here?

37
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:14,960
You're dressed so fine.

38
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,840
Think you're really a Miss Bai?

39
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:18,840
Take it off. You don't deserve to wear this.

40
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,160
What? Scared?

41
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:21,360
So you do know fear.

42
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:23,410
Aren't you the best at pretending?

43
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:25,480
Don't.

44
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:28,000
Didn't you say you weren't a bastard?

45
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:29,000
Then say it.

46
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:30,120
Who gave birth to you?

47
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:31,200
Can't say it, can you?

48
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:32,360
I'm not a bastard.

49
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,760
I am a daughter of the Bai family.

50
00:03:33,760 --> 00:03:35,440
You don't belong here.

51
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:36,520
You are a mistake.

52
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,200
Unwanted.

53
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:38,200
A joke.

54
00:03:38,200 --> 00:03:39,920
The Bai family has no one like you.

55
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:40,640
Enough!

56
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:48,160
Bastard. Bastard. Bastard.

57
00:03:48,160 --> 00:03:49,920
I am not.

58
00:03:58,040 --> 00:03:59,240
Miss Shen is here.

59
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:01,000
Didn't you ask me to come?

60
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:03,880
I heard something about you recently.

61
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:08,330
My father plans to give me to Bulei.

62
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:11,120
Since you know everything, Miss Shen,

63
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,380
why didn't you tell me?

64
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:15,250
I didn't come here for your snide remarks.

65
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:18,720
Telling the truth all the time takes the fun out of things.

66
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:21,560
Aren't you afraid, Miss Shen?

67
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,020
Afraid of what?

68
00:04:24,760 --> 00:04:26,000
Like I said before,

69
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:29,440
if Lord Shen gets my Royal Brother's support,

70
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:31,320
he'll bite you first.

71
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:35,000
Do you think that will happen?

72
00:04:35,440 --> 00:04:37,800
I just hope you can prepare for a rainy day.

73
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:41,490
After all, if someone like my Royal Brother gains power,

74
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:44,600
women are just tools to him.

75
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:47,680
Bulei will regret making this deal with my father.

76
00:04:48,520 --> 00:04:52,520
I said, I'll hurt anyone who hurts me.

77
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:55,840
You aren't planning to turn against Lord Shen now, are you?

78
00:04:55,840 --> 00:04:57,000
You can't win.

79
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,280
I don't need to win.

80
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:02,450
I just need to make him hurt.

81
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:05,880
Do you need me to lend you a knife?

82
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:08,360
Your knife is too expensive.

83
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:09,360
It's not worth it.

84
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:12,940
You just need to stand a bit further away.

85
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,640
Don't get blood on yourself.

86
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:17,090
Remember to tell me before you make a move.

87
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,130
I like watching a good show.

88
00:05:21,440 --> 00:05:24,400
By the will of Heaven, the Emperor decrees.

89
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:27,400
Shen Qiangwei, daughter of Prime Minister Shen,

90
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:28,760
is gentle and virtuous,

91
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,480
and dignified in conduct.

92
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:30,880
His Majesty

93
00:05:30,880 --> 00:05:33,320
hereby bestows upon her the title of Noble Consort.

94
00:05:33,320 --> 00:05:36,360
She shall enter the palace on a selected day to serve the Emperor.

95
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:38,000
Respect this.

96
00:05:39,080 --> 00:05:40,159
Noble Consort?

97
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:42,159
Congratulations, Miss Shen.

98
00:05:42,159 --> 00:05:45,760
From this day forth, you will be Her Highness, the Noble Consort.

99
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:51,480
No, no.

100
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:53,520
Shouldn't I be the Third Prince's Consort?

101
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:55,580
Miss Shen, the edict has been issued.

102
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:58,780
Please prepare to enter the palace as soon as possible.

103
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:17,080
Was it you?

104
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:18,920
Did you sabotage this?

105
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:22,040
Princess Tuoya was clearly just chosen as a consort.

106
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,840
Why would the Emperor choose me?

107
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:26,420
Didn't you always want wealth and glory?

108
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:28,560
Now that you've become the Emperor's Noble Consort,

109
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,820
why are you blaming me?

110
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:30,860
I don't want to.

111
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:33,280
I don't want to marry an old man.

112
00:06:33,280 --> 00:06:37,000
Do you think you have a choice under imperial power?

113
00:06:40,320 --> 00:06:42,360
Shen Qiangwei, I told you.

114
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:44,700
Don't mess with me.

115
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,280
Qiangwei.

116
00:06:54,080 --> 00:06:56,120
Why didn't you stop Shen Lingbo?

117
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:59,050
You knew I didn't want to enter the palace.

118
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:01,400
The situation in the court is critical.

119
00:07:01,400 --> 00:07:02,480
I had no choice.

120
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:05,970
You promised to let me be the Third Prince's Consort.

121
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:07,200
Get out.

122
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:20,480
Qiangwei, go back for now.

123
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:31,120
Father.

124
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:35,320
You'd better think clearly before you act.

125
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:36,920
She is your sister.

126
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:40,680
What you're doing is too vicious.

127
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:44,300
You were the one who sent me away as a bargaining chip first.

128
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:46,490
And now you blame me for learning fast?

129
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:49,640
Everything you have now, I earned for you.

130
00:07:50,159 --> 00:07:52,690
What right do you have to order me around here?

131
00:07:55,159 --> 00:07:56,320
I regret it.

132
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:59,320
I regret letting you into the family back then.

133
00:07:59,320 --> 00:08:01,000
What's the use of regretting now?

134
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:03,460
From the moment you decided to sacrifice me,

135
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:04,920
you had no way back.

136
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:07,010
I did it for the Shen family.

137
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,480
For the whole clan.

138
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:10,050
Then did you ever ask me?

139
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:11,520
Ask if I was willing?

140
00:08:12,400 --> 00:08:15,120
You always say you're planning for the big picture.

141
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:16,440
You can see others,

142
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:19,920
but you've never treated me like a human being.

143
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:23,160
Lingbo, you are my daughter.

144
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:25,520
So I can be abandoned and used?

145
00:08:26,640 --> 00:08:28,900
If you had shown me even a shred of warmth,

146
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:31,600
it wouldn't have come to this today.

147
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:33,520
What do you want?

148
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:38,840
I want you to watch your favorite daughter enter the palace crying.

149
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:42,720
I want you to kneel and beg me, knowing it won't change the past.

150
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:44,880
Must you do this?

151
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:50,040
Father, you taught me this.

152
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:53,040
The weak are prey to the strong.

153
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:55,440
Father, you are old.

154
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:57,170
Your methods are outdated.

155
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:58,400
You can't beat me.

156
00:08:59,640 --> 00:09:01,300
I'll give you one more chance.

157
00:09:02,040 --> 00:09:03,400
Retire in peace.

158
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:12,760
I'll leave the rest to you.

159
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:16,840
Deal with the children in the academy as you see fit.

160
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:19,920
But they are all children of Dasheng officials.

161
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:21,720
The more chaotic Dasheng becomes,

162
00:09:21,720 --> 00:09:23,400
the closer I am to what I want.

163
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:25,480
Watch out for Song Xuan.

164
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:26,810
Don't leave any traces.

165
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:27,600
Yes.
